Hey, chief.

479
00:45:30,552 --> 00:45:31,583
你好
Hello.

480
00:45:32,762 --> 00:45:34,090
你好？
Hello?

481
00:45:34,681 --> 00:45:37,172
這個人開了八百英里來見你
That's all you got to say to this guy that just drove...

482
00:45:37,267 --> 00:45:39,805
