- 你欠我們的！
- 我他媽的什麼都不欠你們。
- You owe us!
- I don't owe you a goddamn thing.

490
00:46:11,764 --> 00:46:14,433
你知道你那混蛋朋友想讓我幹什麼嗎？
Do you know what your asshole friend here wants me to do?

491
00:46:14,767 --> 00:46:18,717
搶銀行！你相信麼？他媽的銀行！
Rob a fucking bank! Can you believe it? A fucking bank!

492
00:46:19,856 --> 00:46:22,098
他還說那是「政治運動」
A "political action," he calls it.

493
00:46:22,359 --> 00:46:25,313
自由軍佈置給我們這個任務的
We've been assigned this little job by the Liberation Army.

494
00:46:25,404 --> 00:46:28,274
別人都對他們有錯誤的印象，以為他們在支持我們……
Who are under the mistaken impression that they've been supporting us...

495
00:46:28,365 --> 00:46:30,025
我們欠他們的！
and we owe them something!

496
00:46:31,035 --> 00:46:33,111
你想讓我的孩子做什麼？
What do they want my kids to do?

497
00:46:33,204 --> 00:46:35,576
推翻他媽的總統？
Knock off the fucking president?

498
00:46:36,416 --> 00:46:38,455
你想讓我看看你車裡是什麼嗎？
You want to show what you got in your car?

499
00:46:39,586 --> 00:46:41,709
沒什麼。我的東西。
Nothing. It's my stuff.

500
00:46:42,047 --> 00:46:44,253
這可不是你給我的印象。
That's not the impression you gave me.

501
00:46:44,716 --> 00:46:47,041
看看吧，怎麼樣？
Let's look, shall we?

502
00:46:47,761 --> 00:46:49,385
讓孩子們過來。我想讓他們看看這個。
Get the kids down here.I want them to see this.

503
00:46:49,472 --> 00:46:51,429
這人還他媽是個瘋子！
guy's still a fucking maniac!

504
00:46:51,516 --> 00:46:52,547
閉嘴吧
Just stop it.

505
00:46:52,642 --> 00:46:55,726
孩子們！過來！就現在！
Boys! Get down here! Now!

506
00:47:18,462 --> 00:47:22,460
我想讓你們知道，我們不動槍
I want you to know guns are not what we're about.

507
00:47:26,721 --> 00:47:28,345
現在，回屋裡去
Now, get back in the house.

508
00:47:39,026 --> 00:47:41,149
你會改變世界的，阿瑟……
You're going to change the world, Artie...

509
00:47:42,071 --> 00:47:45,238
就組織一下那幾個小食品公司？
by organizing these little food co-ops?

510
00:47:48,578 --> 00:47:49,906
我要出去。
I'm going out.

511
00:47:51,999 --> 00:47:53,659
你晚上可以留下……
You can stay the night...

512
00:47:53,751 --> 00:47:57,914
但等我回來，我可不想看見這些槍在我孩子周圍十公里以內。
but when I get back, I don't want to see these things within 10 miles of my kids.

513
00:48:17,860 --> 00:48:20,185
安妮，我想解釋
Annie, I'd like to explain this.

514
00:48:21,573 --> 00:48:22,901
我在聽。
I'm listening.

515
00:48:25,202 --> 00:48:27,527
你知道，我們在地下狀態已經很久了
You know, we've been under a long time.

516
00:48:28,539 --> 00:48:32,537
很多不好的事情發生了。很多不好的事情還在發生。
A lot of bad shit has happened. A lot of bad shit keeps happening.

517
00:48:34,545 --> 00:48:36,039
但是整個世界都以為
But we're dead...

518
00:48:39,551 --> 00:48:43,002
我們已經死了
as far as the world is concerned.

519
00:48:43,096 --> 00:48:45,587
我們採取一個行動，報紙就埋沒一個
We pull an action and they bury it in the newspapers.

520
00:48:46,308 --> 00:48:48,300
就好像什麼都沒發生過
It's like it didn't happen.

521
00:48:49,103 --> 00:48:51,973
只有在什麼東西或者什麼人被吹走了
The only time the pigs or the media pay attention...

522
00:48:52,065 --> 00:48:55,149
那豬一樣的媒體才會引起注意
is when something or somebody gets blown away.

523
00:48:56,194 --> 00:48:59,527
好。如果打不敗他們，就加入他們。
Great. If you can't beat them, join them.

524
00:49:00,365 --> 00:49:04,528
你覺得我們採取非暴力，會取得勝利麼？
Do you think we're going to win this by turning the other cheek?

525
00:49:06,372 --> 00:49:08,495
要是能這樣，你怎麼不試試在水上走？
Why don't you try walking on water?

526
00:49:08,583 --> 00:49:11,916
你怎麼還不長大呢？我們贏不了的。
Why don't you try growing up? There's nothing to win.

527
00:49:12,754 --> 00:49:14,746
戰爭一結束，它已經結束了。
It was over as soon as the war ended.

528
00:49:15,549 --> 00:49:19,381
戰爭沒有結束，安妮。它永遠不會結束。
The war didn't end, Annie.The war ain't never going to end.

529
00:49:19,553 --> 00:49:24,511
和政治或者我車裡的貨無關。
This has nothing to do with politics or the merchandise in my car.

530
00:49:24,600 --> 00:49:26,557
只是阿瑟發火了
This is just Artie's pissed.

531
00:49:29,564 --> 00:49:31,106
阿瑟發火了……
Artie's pissed...

532
00:49:32,150 --> 00:49:33,608
是因為他嫉妒。
'cause Artie's jealous.

533
00:49:36,030 --> 00:49:38,022
他嫉妒……
And Artie's jealous...

534
00:49:41,536 --> 00:49:43,244
是因為你想要我。
because you want me.

535
00:49:44,706 --> 00:49:46,366
我當然也想要你
And I sure want you.

536
00:49:50,712 --> 00:49:52,539
這狀況真糟糕。
That's a bad situation.

537
00:49:55,426 --> 00:49:58,095
遲早它們都會爆炸
Sooner or later, they're just going to blow up.

538
00:50:02,392 --> 00:50:04,384
你知道，我為你感到遺憾
You know, I feel sorry for you.

539
00:50:04,769 --> 00:50:05,931
真的。
I do.

540
00:50:06,605 --> 00:50:08,597
你46歲了，還像個嬰兒
You're a 46-year-old infant.

541
00:50:10,109 --> 00:50:14,771
什麼都得按著你的想法來，是不是？什麼時候都是，什麼地方都是
Everything has to be your way, doesn't it? When you want it, where you want it.

542
00:50:16,908 --> 00:50:18,699
你不是革命者
You're not a revolutionary.

543
00:50:18,785 --> 00:50:23,114
這比玩槍或者玩弄自己要求更高
That requires more than playing with guns or with yourself.

544
00:50:24,958 --> 00:50:27,912
需要同情心，需要紀律
It requires compassion, discipline.

545
00:50:28,003 --> 00:50:30,245
你在評判我麼？
Are you judging me?

546
00:50:37,055 --> 00:50:39,213
女士，你在評判你自己。
You judge yourself, lady.

547
00:50:40,726 --> 00:50:44,889
你過得就像那種傻乎乎的中產階級的郊區家庭主婦
You're living like some kind of silly-ass, middle-class, suburban housewife.

548
00:50:48,234 --> 00:50:49,894
你活在謊言之中……
You're living a lie...

549
00:50:50,903 --> 00:50:52,895
就像你說的那樣。
just like you said.

550
00:50:55,075 --> 00:50:59,903
你為什麼不把諾曼·洛克威爾一家供出來？
Why don't you take this little Norman Rockwell family and turn them in?

551
00:51:01,248 --> 00:51:03,121
聯邦調查局會很樂意抓到他們的。
The feds would be glad to get them.

552
00:51:04,418 --> 00:51:05,912
這樣你就可以脫身了。
And then you could get the fuck out.

553
00:51:09,591 --> 00:51:10,919
我倒希望我能。
I wish I could.

554
00:51:13,595 --> 00:51:15,089
出去吧。
Now get out.

555
00:51:42,627 --> 00:51:44,002
你還好麼，媽媽
Are you okay, Mom?

556
00:51:45,839 --> 00:51:46,870
嗯。
Yeah.

557
00:51:47,883 --> 00:51:49,128
好。
Fine.

558
00:52:06,361 --> 00:52:07,689
睡覺吧。
Go to bed.

559
00:52:53,580 --> 00:52:57,245
我不是保羅！我不是保羅！我是……
I am not Paul. I am not Paul! I am-

560
00:53:00,462 --> 00:53:03,416
- 進來，保羅。
- 我不是保羅！
- Paul, come in.
- I'm not Paul.

561
00:53:03,716 --> 00:53:04,961
我是阿瑟
I'm Arthur.

562
00:53:05,384 --> 00:53:07,756
別叫我「保羅」。我是阿瑟。
Don't call me "Paul. " I am Arthur.

563
00:53:08,304 --> 00:53:11,139
我是阿瑟·艾利·波普！
I am Arthur Eli Pope!

564
00:53:12,058 --> 00:53:14,549
- 爸爸怎麼了？
- 他剛喝多了。
- What's the matter with Dad?
- He's just had a lot to drink.

565
00:53:14,645 --> 00:53:19,603
1944年7月16日出生在紐約州的普拉茨堡！
Born in Plattsburg, New York, July 16, 1944!

566
00:53:20,151 --> 00:53:22,642
美國公民……我母親……
A US citizen. My mother's...

567
00:53:23,363 --> 00:53:25,688
娘家姓是希爾伯維茨。
maiden name is Silbowitz.

568
00:53:25,949 --> 00:53:29,448
我父親真名是波波夫。莫裡斯·波波夫。
My father's real name is Popov.Morris Popov.

569
00:53:30,787 --> 00:53:33,456
我駕駛證號碼是4-3-5-7...
My driver's license number is 4-3-5-7...

570
00:53:34,208 --> 00:53:35,370
1-1。
1-1.

571
00:53:36,419 --> 00:53:39,206
我入伍時候的號碼是M-S-8-9...
My draft number is M-S-8-9...

572
00:53:39,464 --> 00:53:42,963
- 3-5-8-4.
- 好了。
-3-5-8-4.
- It's okay.

573
00:53:43,968 --> 00:53:45,960
我叫波普。
My name is Pope.

574
00:53:46,096 --> 00:53:47,210
沒事了。
It's okay.

575
00:54:16,379 --> 00:54:18,537
你說要散步，又不是遠足。
You said walk, not hike.

576
00:54:20,050 --> 00:54:21,877
- 你累了？
- 不是。
- Are you tired?
- No.

577
00:54:28,559 --> 00:54:31,050
- 很美。
- 是啊。
-It's beautiful.
- Yeah.

578
00:54:34,065 --> 00:54:36,390
你知道，當你約我的時候我真的很驚訝
You know, I was really surprised when you called me.

579
00:54:37,652 --> 00:54:38,766
為什麼？
Why?

580
00:54:39,571 --> 00:54:42,062
我不確定你是不是喜歡我
I wasn't sure if you liked me or not.

581
00:54:43,075 --> 00:54:45,780
有的時候你那麼……
Sometimes you're so...

582
00:54:50,083 --> 00:54:53,618
我也不確定你是不是也很喜歡我。
I'm not too sure if you like me too much, either.

583
00:54:55,172 --> 00:54:59,335
相信吧。我可不會跟著一個我不喜歡的人走上十英里
Take it on faith. I usually don't follow people I don't like for 10 miles...

584
00:54:59,426 --> 00:55:00,920
一直走到樹林中間
into the middle of the woods.

585
00:55:01,011 --> 00:55:02,505
你怎麼這麼生氣？
Why are you so angry?

586
00:55:03,347 --> 00:55:05,090
那是風趣，不是生氣
That's wit, not anger.

587
00:55:06,184 --> 00:55:09,054
- 你嚇到很多人。
- 除了你還有誰？
- You scare a lot of people.
- Who, besides you?

588
00:55:13,525 --> 00:55:15,482
很多人嚇到我。
A lot of people scare me.

589
00:55:15,569 --> 00:55:17,193
誰嚇到你？
Who scares you?

590
00:55:22,243 --> 00:55:25,244
像我父母一樣和善的人
People who are nice, like my parents.

591
00:55:26,915 --> 00:55:28,907
和善的人有什麼錯？
What's wrong with being nice?

592
00:55:29,584 --> 00:55:31,576
這樣說吧。
Let's put it like this.

593
00:55:32,504 --> 00:55:34,911
我母親真的很好。
My mother is really nice.

594
00:55:35,383 --> 00:55:38,550
她從來不做任何錯事或者刻薄的事
She never does anything wrong or mean.

595
00:55:40,179 --> 00:55:42,467
她甚至把舊衣服給僕人
She even gives her old clothe to the maid...

596
00:55:42,557 --> 00:55:45,842
但她真的不想認識她
but she doesn't really want to know her.

597
00:55:45,936 --> 00:55:48,605
十年裡她連貝蒂的丈夫都沒見過
In 10 years,she's never even seen Betty's husband.

598
00:55:49,815 --> 00:55:52,306
他來接她的時候都在車裡等著
He waits in the car when he comes to pick her up.

599
00:55:55,321 --> 00:55:57,397
你父親一定不像這樣
Your father's sure not like that.

600
00:55:57,657 --> 00:55:59,614
為什麼？因為他在課上放麥當娜的歌？
Why? Because he plays Madonna in class?

601
00:55:59,701 --> 00:56:02,536
他除了知道你彈琴很棒，還知道什麼？
What does he know about you, except that you're good on the piano?

602
00:56:03,038 --> 00:56:06,323
他們只看到他們想看的東西，把別的都屏蔽掉
They see what they want to see,and they block out everything else...

603
00:56:06,417 --> 00:56:08,824
尤其是可能不太好的東西
especially if it might not be nice.

604
00:56:10,171 --> 00:56:12,128
他們好像並不很習慣你的方式
They don't seem to get in your way much.

605
00:56:12,215 --> 00:56:15,584
我父母？他們的方式就是不相信我真正的樣子
My parents? It's just their way of not believing who I really am.

606
00:56:15,760 --> 00:56:18,333
他們覺得最終我會變成
They think that eventually,I'll turn back into the little girl...

607
00:56:18,430 --> 00:56:21,384
鋼琴上的照片裡那穿著粉色裙子的小女孩
in the pink dress that's in the picture on the piano.

608
00:56:24,395 --> 00:56:25,889
那你覺得呢？
And what do you think?

609
00:56:26,564 --> 00:56:28,307
你真的想知道？
You really want to know?

610
00:56:28,566 --> 00:56:32,398
你覺得我會去紐約學寫作
I think that I'll go to New York and learn to write...

611
00:56:32,654 --> 00:56:34,979
每個聖誕節回家
and that I'll come home every Christmas...

612
00:56:35,240 --> 00:56:38,075
大家都對我很禮貌
and everyone will be really polite.

613
00:56:39,244 --> 00:56:41,236
聽起來沒那麼壞。
That's doesn't sound so bad.

614
00:56:42,498 --> 00:56:44,989
也許是，但是我還沒真正在紐約
Maybe not, but I'm not in New York yet.

615
00:56:51,424 --> 00:56:52,704
那你呢？
So what about you?

616
00:56:54,386 --> 00:56:56,295
我完全不瞭解你
I don't know a thing about you.

617
00:56:56,388 --> 00:56:59,721
你可能會完好地從宙斯的腦袋裡鑽出來（指雅典娜）
You might as well have sprung full-grown out of the head of Zeus.

618
00:57:00,393 --> 00:57:02,551
那你父母呢？奧茲和哈里特？（電影《奧茲和哈里特的冒險》，奧茲和哈里特生活在數字時代）
Who are your parents? Ozzie and Harriet?

619
00:57:02,895 --> 00:57:04,555
是啊，有時候是這樣
Yeah, sometimes.

620
00:57:05,398 --> 00:57:07,723
我是不是得去見見他們，看看你為什麼這麼完美？
Do I get to meet them and see how you came out so perfect?

621
00:57:07,817 --> 00:57:09,275
我的意思是，這樣才公平
I mean, it seems only fair.

622
00:57:10,195 --> 00:57:12,483
我讓你看我的，你讓我看你的
I showed you mine, you show me yours.

623
00:57:18,245 --> 00:57:20,403
我猜這就結束休息了吧
I guess this is the end of the rest stop.

624
00:57:23,918 --> 00:57:25,578
我說什麼來著？
What did I say?

625
00:57:28,006 --> 00:57:30,331
我以為下面會好一些
I thought it would be nicer down here.

626
00:57:32,094 --> 00:57:34,763
你沒傳達太多信息
You don't transmit too much information.

627
00:57:35,598 --> 00:57:36,629
什麼？
What?

628
00:57:37,099 --> 00:57:40,016
我說，你沒傳達太多信息
I said, you don't transmit too much information.

629
00:57:40,166 --> 00:57:41,216
對不起。
Sorry.

630
00:57:43,116 --> 00:57:45,273
你夏天要幹什麼？
What are you doing over the summer?

631
00:57:47,285 --> 00:57:49,609
我在加油站找了份工作
I have a job pumping gas.

632
00:57:49,954 --> 00:57:52,787
你終於讓最高法院聽你的了，嗯？
You finally got the Supreme Court to hear your case, huh?

633
00:57:55,793 --> 00:57:57,286
你呢？
What about you?

634
00:57:58,629 --> 00:57:59,956
不知道。
I don't know.

635
00:58:02,466 --> 00:58:04,457
你覺得在這更好？
You thought it'd be nicer over here?

636
00:58:06,636 --> 00:58:07,666
嗯
Yeah.

637
00:58:16,979 --> 00:58:18,353
你在幹什麼
What are you doing?

638
00:58:21,483 --> 00:58:24,435
找點什麼送我媽媽生日禮物
I'm looking for something for my mom's birthday.

639
00:58:26,571 --> 00:58:28,028
你的意思是說，萬一有人偶爾在沙灘上丟了
You mean, in case somebody happened to leave...

640
00:58:28,113 --> 00:58:29,938
一個Cuisinart（美國廚具品牌）的東西或者一個鑽石戒指？
a Cuisinart or a diamond ring lying on the beach?

