00:58:30,324 --> 00:58:33,489
是啊，那就行。必須得是你做的，或者是你找到的東西。
Yeah, that would qualify. It has to be omething either you make or find.

642
00:58:33,577 --> 00:58:36,113
- 她生日是什麼時候？
- 下周。
- When's her birthday?
- Next week.

643
00:58:58,057 --> 00:58:59,550
真美。
That's beautiful.

644
00:59:01,728 --> 00:59:03,386
給你媽媽的。
It's for your mother.

645
00:59:06,065 --> 00:59:07,558
你送給她。
You give it to her.

646
00:59:10,277 --> 00:59:11,307
好
Okay.

647
00:59:15,323 --> 00:59:16,899
在那一定更好。
It must be nicer over there.

648
00:59:19,160 --> 00:59:21,317
過來，切這些。
Here, chop these.

649
00:59:31,129 --> 00:59:34,212
不對，不對，不對。看。你到一邊去。
No, no, no. Watch. Move.

650
00:59:34,798 --> 00:59:36,540
拿著刀……
You hold the knife...

651
00:59:36,634 --> 00:59:38,791
就這麼做。
and you just do that.

652
00:59:39,136 --> 00:59:40,545
很乾淨。我試試
That's neat. Let me try.

653
00:59:40,637 --> 00:59:45,131
不，不。我是個素食者，我可不想你把你的小手指頭切到菜裡去。
No, no. I'm a vegetarian. I don't want pieces of tiny little fingers in my stew.

654
00:59:45,225 --> 00:59:46,552
這。你來攪拌。
Here. You stir.

655
00:59:49,062 --> 00:59:50,852
你在等誰嗎？
Were you expecting someone?

656
00:59:59,446 --> 01:00:00,476
嗨。
Hi.

657
01:00:02,073 --> 01:00:03,400
我是羅娜。
I'm Lorna.

658
01:00:04,659 --> 01:00:06,317
麥克邀請了我。
Michael invited me.

659
01:00:07,662 --> 01:00:09,487
好吧，進來吧
Well, come in.

660
01:00:15,419 --> 01:00:16,912
你朋友在這
Your friend's here.

661
01:00:18,422 --> 01:00:19,452
嗨
Hi.

662
01:00:22,467 --> 01:00:24,257
- 嗨。
- 我可以幫忙麼？
- Hi.
- Can I help?

663
01:00:24,635 --> 01:00:26,959
不用，不用，沒關係。謝謝。
No. No, it's okay. Thank you.

664
01:00:27,471 --> 01:00:28,964
你切到手指了。
You cut your finger.

665
01:00:29,056 --> 01:00:30,086
是啊
Yeah.

666
01:00:30,599 --> 01:00:32,424
這是你女朋友？
Is this your girlfriend?

667
01:00:32,768 --> 01:00:34,593
嗨，我是史蒂芬。
Hi, I'm Stephen.

668
01:00:37,606 --> 01:00:40,558
真好吃，寶貝。完全超出你的水平
That was delicious, babe.You outdid yourself.

669
01:00:40,650 --> 01:00:43,982
為我自己的安格魯-撒克遜教徒準備的朝聖食物。
This pilgrim food for my very own WASP.

670
01:00:44,570 --> 01:00:46,312
但是你得原諒我，親愛的
But you must forgive me, my darling.

671
01:00:46,405 --> 01:00:48,894
我沒法做出這種果凍模具
I couldn't get myself to make one of those Jell-O molds.

672
01:00:50,659 --> 01:00:52,401
這次就原諒你了
You're forgiven this time.

673
01:00:52,494 --> 01:00:54,983
現在，（法語）
And now, for the pi鎗e de r閟istance.

674
01:00:55,247 --> 01:00:58,412
- 我來，爸爸
- 你被逮捕了
- Let me, Dad.
- You're under arrest.

675
01:01:08,174 --> 01:01:10,414
看看，你弄得肚臍那到處都是
Look at this.You got it all over your bellybutton.

676
01:01:10,510 --> 01:01:12,168
看看
Look at that.

677
01:01:12,637 --> 01:01:16,300
哦天哪。我老得都能把這房子弄著火。
Oh, God. I'm old enough to set the house on fire.

678
01:01:39,578 --> 01:01:42,494
抱歉，我以為你媽媽叫辛西婭。
I'm sorry, I thought your mother's name was Cynthia.

679
01:01:42,831 --> 01:01:44,822
過生日的時候我們都叫山姆
On birthdays, we're all Sam.

680
01:01:45,125 --> 01:01:46,534
這是我們家小小的傳統……
It's a little family tradition...

681
01:01:46,626 --> 01:01:50,289
是因為我1968年那次超棒的用迷幻劑的經歷
resulting from a particularly good LSD trip I took in 1968.

682
01:01:53,799 --> 01:01:55,126
再來點酒？
More wine?

683
01:01:56,677 --> 01:01:59,510
- 你能讓我歇會麼？
- 在歐洲，小孩子就能喝酒。
- Would you give me a break?
- In Europe, kids drink wine.

684
01:01:59,596 --> 01:02:03,924
在我給「匿名酗酒者（美國一家幫助戒酒的機構）」打電話（指喝醉）之前，把給你媽媽的禮物拿來。
Get your mother her present before I call Alcoholics Anonymous.

685
01:02:13,233 --> 01:02:14,263
謝謝
Thanks.

686
01:02:19,948 --> 01:02:22,864
這就是我想要的
It's just what I wanted.

687
01:02:22,951 --> 01:02:25,275
- 真的？
- 千真萬確
- Really?
- Absolutely.

688
01:02:29,624 --> 01:02:31,414
那是什麼，蝴蝶？
What is that, a butterfly?

689
01:02:31,500 --> 01:02:33,787
不是，是個鯨魚，當做禮物了
No, it's a whale of a present.

690
01:02:41,300 --> 01:02:43,042
- 謝謝
- 我會彈奏它的
- Thanks.- I'll play it for you sometime.

691
01:02:44,011 --> 01:02:46,500
這是羅娜的禮物
This is from Lorna.

692
01:02:54,354 --> 01:02:56,012
真美
That's beautiful.

693
01:02:56,939 --> 01:02:58,597
謝謝你，羅娜
Thank you, Lorna.

694
01:03:01,527 --> 01:03:03,684
我的禮物，等會給你
Mine, you get later.

695
01:03:04,196 --> 01:03:05,357
你保證
You bet.

696
01:03:06,365 --> 01:03:07,692
沒問題
On your feet!

697
01:03:07,949 --> 01:03:09,276
我來幫忙。
Let me help.

698
01:03:11,536 --> 01:03:13,029
我喜歡她。
I like her.

699
01:03:13,121 --> 01:03:14,199
嗯？
Yeah?

700
01:03:14,289 --> 01:03:16,613
- 我也喜歡她。
- 我知道
- I like her, too.- I know.

701
01:04:12,299 --> 01:04:14,586
你確定這是菲利普斯家的孩子？
You sure this is the Phillips' kid?

702
01:04:14,843 --> 01:04:17,415
你在醫院沒被掉包吧，嗯？
They didn't switch you at the hospital,or anything, did they?

703
01:05:15,773 --> 01:05:18,808
你知道，我不敢想像他們有多不可理喻。
You know, I can't believe how incredible they are.

704
01:05:19,151 --> 01:05:24,310
你知道如果我給我媽媽一個貝殼當做生日禮物，她會怎麼做？
Do you know what my mother would do if I gave her a shell for her birthday?

705
01:05:24,739 --> 01:05:26,397
沒關係吧
They're okay.

706
01:05:27,325 --> 01:05:30,158
那就是你，害怕承認自己
That's you all over,afraid to commit yourself.

707
01:05:31,078 --> 01:05:32,903
我以為這就是我
I thought it was just me.

708
01:05:37,167 --> 01:05:38,957
和你在一起我很開心
I'm very happy with you.

709
01:05:41,588 --> 01:05:43,828
我也是
I'm very happy with you, too.

710
01:06:42,100 --> 01:06:44,174
沒關係，我想這樣
It's okay, I want to.

711
01:07:36,441 --> 01:07:38,930
- 你沒去上廚藝課
- 你注意到了。
- You weren't in cooking.
- You noticed.

712
01:07:39,444 --> 01:07:41,435
- 你去哪了？
- 我翹課了
- Where were you?- I cut.

713
01:07:43,156 --> 01:07:45,527
- 為什麼？
- 我不想見你。
- Why?- I didn't want to see you.

714
01:08:08,345 --> 01:08:11,344
曼菲爾德，我能和你說幾句話麼
Manfield, could I talk to you for a minute?

715
01:08:16,352 --> 01:08:19,020
你沒必要這麼緊張。就算你做了錯事……
You don't have to look so anxious.If you've done something wrong...

716
01:08:19,105 --> 01:08:22,140
我也不知道。我只是想知道你對大學的計劃。
I don't know about it. I just want to talk to you about your college plans.

717
01:08:22,233 --> 01:08:26,229
我想休息一年，也許去歐洲旅行，聽聽音樂。
I was thinking of taking a year off, maybe traveling to Europe, listening to music.

718
01:08:26,320 --> 01:08:29,818
我不能要求你做什麼，但是我覺得你應該申請大學
I can't tell you what to do, but I think you ought to make an application, anyway.

719
01:08:29,906 --> 01:08:31,862
你可以推遲入學的
You can always postpone entry.

720
01:08:31,949 --> 01:08:34,320
我想讓你考慮考慮申請朱利亞德（紐約一所藝術學院）
I'd like you to consider applying to Juilliard.

721
01:08:34,410 --> 01:08:35,951
提前錄取
Early admission.

722
01:08:39,790 --> 01:08:43,703
我看了你成績的檔案，被錄取應該沒問題
I looked at your academic records.You should have no trouble getting in.

723
01:08:44,086 --> 01:08:45,283
不過，剩下的呢？
Where's the rest of it, by the way?

724
01:08:45,379 --> 01:08:47,417
你的檔案裡沒有原先的學校的。
There's nothing in your file from your old school.

725
01:08:49,132 --> 01:08:51,289
我們搬家的時候弄丟了。
It was lost when we moved.

726
01:08:52,634 --> 01:08:54,127
找回來的時候，我想看看。
When it comes through, I'd like to see it.

727
01:08:55,387 --> 01:08:57,378
同時，你看看這個。
In the meantime, you look at that.

728
01:09:02,477 --> 01:09:04,598
我會樂意給你寫推薦信的。
I'd be happy to write you a letter of recommendation.

729
01:09:05,313 --> 01:09:06,556
謝謝
Thank you.

730
01:09:09,651 --> 01:09:12,057
看完之後還給我
Get back to me when you've looked at it.

731
01:10:17,587 --> 01:10:19,578
你不和我說話
You wouldn't talk to me.

732
01:10:22,090 --> 01:10:23,417
現在，起床
Now, get up.

733
01:10:23,800 --> 01:10:26,289
下樓，從後門出去
Go down the stairs and out the back door.

734
01:10:26,803 --> 01:10:28,296
悄悄的
Be quiet.

735
01:10:38,147 --> 01:10:39,972
我就在你後面。
I'll be right behind you.

736
01:10:52,701 --> 01:10:54,359
我光著腳呢
I'm barefoot.

737
01:11:26,857 --> 01:11:28,018
坐下
Sit down.

738
01:11:36,991 --> 01:11:38,532
我在幹嘛？
What am I doing?

739
01:11:42,371 --> 01:11:44,409
我就是想和你說話。
I just wanted to talk to you.

740
01:11:46,667 --> 01:11:48,991
你那天在學校不聽我講。
You wouldn't listen, the other day at school.

741
01:11:55,174 --> 01:11:59,751
我那天晚上沒和你在一起，不是因為我不想。
I couldn't stay with you that night. Not because I didn't want to.

742
01:12:09,563 --> 01:12:11,887
如果你想回去，對我來說沒什麼。
If you want to go back, it's fine with me.

743
01:12:13,774 --> 01:12:15,979
- 你是個笨蛋。
- 不。
- You're a bully.- No.

744
01:12:19,571 --> 01:12:21,028
我說了謊。
I'm a liar.

745
01:12:24,576 --> 01:12:26,234
我真名不是麥克
My name isn't Michael.

746
01:12:28,705 --> 01:12:29,818
是丹尼。
It's Danny.

747
01:12:31,332 --> 01:12:35,079
我父母是阿瑟和安妮·波普
My parents are Arthur and Annie Pope.

748
01:12:37,504 --> 01:12:41,832
1971年他們因為讓汽油彈實驗室爆炸，和聯邦調查局惹上了麻煩
They're in trouble with the FBl for blowing up a napalm lab in 1971.

749
01:12:41,925 --> 01:12:43,797
有一個人差點就死了
There was a man who was almost killed.

750
01:12:43,885 --> 01:12:45,793
那是個看門人，當時不該在那的
A janitor,abcwho wasn't supposed to be there.

751
01:12:45,887 --> 01:12:48,803
我們在所有生日蛋糕上都寫「山姆」
We put "Sam" on the birthday cakes, on all the birthday cakes...

752
01:12:49,682 --> 01:12:52,136
是因為每到一個地方，我們就換新名字
because we change our names every time we move.

753
01:12:55,104 --> 01:12:58,269
從我兩歲起，就一直這樣了
I've been doing this since I was two.

754
01:12:59,315 --> 01:13:01,140
我不知道別的辦法。
I don't know any other way.

755
01:13:01,817 --> 01:13:05,184
我只是想告訴你我很抱歉
I just wanted to tell you that I was sorry.

756
01:13:08,240 --> 01:13:11,572
我想解釋我為什麼說不了太多事
I wanted to explain why I can't talk about a lot of things.

757
01:13:12,161 --> 01:13:15,778
比如大學。我不能去上大學。我不能離開他們。
Like college. I can't go to college.I can't leave them.

758
01:13:19,500 --> 01:13:21,325
我還想告訴你……
And I wanted to tell you...

759
01:13:22,503 --> 01:13:24,209
我為什麼不能和你在一起。
why I couldn't be with you.

760
01:13:25,214 --> 01:13:28,047
不能讓你不知道。我不想對你說謊。
Not without your knowing.I didn't want to lie to you.

761
01:13:30,010 --> 01:13:33,757
現在我沒權利和你說這些的
Now, I have no right in telling this to you.

762
01:13:33,847 --> 01:13:36,680
對你，對他們，都很危險。
It's dangerous for you,and it's dangerous for them.

763
01:13:38,852 --> 01:13:41,057
對不起，我只是控制不住自己
I'm sorry. I just couldn't stop myself.

764
01:13:41,561 --> 01:13:45,142
你想做什麼都可以做，你可以告訴你爸爸。我不介意
You can do what you want to. You can tell your dad anything. I don't care.

765
01:13:46,149 --> 01:13:47,974
我只是想要你知道
I just needed you to know.

766
01:13:49,652 --> 01:13:51,976
我不知道我在做什麼
I don't know what I'm doing.

767
01:13:54,824 --> 01:13:56,067
我愛你
And I love you.

768
01:14:00,663 --> 01:14:01,990
我愛你
I love you.

769
01:14:33,817 --> 01:14:35,310
那我要叫你什麼？
What do I call you?

770
01:14:35,402 --> 01:14:38,437
麥克。什麼都不用變
Michael. Nothing changes.

771
01:14:39,364 --> 01:14:41,688
他們真的不想讓你上大學麼？
They really don't want you to go to school, huh?

772
01:14:44,285 --> 01:14:46,110
我們還沒有談
We haven't talked about it.

773
01:14:46,955 --> 01:14:48,661
- 我不能問他們
- 為什麼不？
- I can't ask them.- Why not?

774
01:14:50,290 --> 01:14:52,958
那就意味著拆散整個家庭，我再也見不到他們。
It would mean breaking up the family,not seeing them again.

775
01:14:54,419 --> 01:14:56,375
他們除了我們，什麼都沒有
They don't have anything else.

776
01:14:57,881 --> 01:15:02,874
我不能相信他們會要求你耗費自己的生命去陪著他們
I can't believe that they'd want you to give up your whole life to stay with them.

777
01:15:03,469 --> 01:15:05,793
和他們談。他們會理解的。
Talk to them. They'll understand.

778
01:15:10,433 --> 01:15:12,590
你有很多秘密，不是麼
You have a lot of secrets, don't you?

779
01:15:14,354 --> 01:15:16,144
現在你又多了一個。
Now you have another one.

780
01:15:57,809 --> 01:15:59,302
去和羅娜約會了？
Been to see Lorna?

781
01:16:09,362 --> 01:16:10,855
我喜歡她。
I like that one.

782
01:16:11,322 --> 01:16:12,980
她很活潑
She's full of beans.

783
01:16:15,701 --> 01:16:17,526
你真心喜歡她，不是麼
You really like her, don't you?

784
01:16:18,870 --> 01:16:21,110
聰明的人總是最好的
The smart ones are always the best.

785
01:16:23,374 --> 01:16:25,080
你和她睡了麼？
Are you sleeping with her?

786
01:16:26,794 --> 01:16:28,868
- 嗯。
- 好。
- Yeah.
- Okay.

787
01:16:30,548 --> 01:16:33,298
快去，睡覺去。明天還要上學。
Go ahead, hit the sack.You got school tomorrow.

788
01:17:42,654 --> 01:17:44,894
你在停止專業鋼琴之後
How long have you been playing violin...

789
01:17:44,990 --> 01:17:48,155
演奏了多久小提琴？
after you stopped playing seriously piano?

790
01:17:48,826 --> 01:17:50,105
大概五年
About five years.

791
01:17:50,202 --> 01:17:51,992
什麼時候來美國的？
When did you come to the States?

792
01:17:52,830 --> 01:17:54,109
1980年
In 1980.

793
01:17:54,206 --> 01:17:56,280
好的，非常感謝
All right. Thank you very much.

794
01:17:56,875 --> 01:17:59,874
曼菲爾德先生，我們準備好面試你了。
Mr. Manfield. We're ready for you now.

795
01:20:31,348 --> 01:20:33,802
你說你和誰學的？
Who did you say you studied with?

796
01:20:35,435 --> 01:20:36,976
愛德華·菲利普斯
Edward Phillips.

797
01:20:37,061 --> 01:20:39,467
- 在哪？
- 沃特福德。
- Where was this?- Waterford.

798
01:20:40,148 --> 01:20:42,305
- 新澤西？
- 對
- New Jersey?- That's right.

799
01:20:42,650 --> 01:20:44,807
我們好像沒有你的學校檔案
We seem not to have all your school records.

800
01:20:46,820 --> 01:20:50,863
我以前的學校有，但是丟了
There was a school fire at my old school, and the records were lost.

801
01:20:51,074 --> 01:20:53,563
今年我們剛搬到新澤西
We only moved to New Jersey this year.

802
01:20:53,993 --> 01:20:58,487
所以你和菲利普斯先生只學了很短時間
So you've only studied with Mr. Phillipsfor a short time.

803
01:20:58,914 --> 01:21:00,241
是的，太太
Yes, ma'am.

804
01:21:00,332 --> 01:21:02,323
你還和誰學過？
Who else have you worked with?

805
01:21:04,545 --> 01:21:07,165
很多不同的，但沒有一個這麼重要
A lot of different people.No one important.

806
01:21:07,588 --> 01:21:09,579
我們經常搬家
We move a lot.

807
01:21:09,882 --> 01:21:13,166
你必須給我們你的SAT成績，還有……
You'll have to supply us with SAT scores and...

808
01:21:14,220 --> 01:21:16,010
我們必須要那些檔案
we'll have to have those records.

809
01:21:20,642 --> 01:21:21,672
曼菲爾德先生。
Mr. Manfield.

810
01:21:22,519 --> 01:21:23,549
哦，對不起
Oh, sorry.

811
01:21:25,564 --> 01:21:29,014
你很有才華，你知道
You are very talented, you know.

812
01:21:31,652 --> 01:21:33,145
謝謝，太太
Thank you, ma'am.

813
01:22:39,838 --> 01:22:42,244
給帕特森太太的芝士比薩。
A cheese pizza for Mrs. Patterson.

814
