- 是
- 那有人定了比薩。
- Yes.- Someone ordered it.

817
01:22:53,560 --> 01:22:54,590
稍等。

818
01:23:05,987 --> 01:23:08,025
這比薩是怎麼回事？

819
01:23:09,699 --> 01:23:11,489
你訂了一個。
You ordered one.

820
01:23:13,035 --> 01:23:14,409
我沒有。
I didn't.

821
01:23:16,497 --> 01:23:18,239
那你得付錢麼？
Will you have to pay for it?

822
01:23:19,540 --> 01:23:21,946
不，我得吃
No, I'll have to eat it.

823
01:23:33,387 --> 01:23:36,422
我真的不在乎。等等。你下次不能敲門麼？
I really don't care. Hold on.Could you knock next time?

824
01:23:36,807 --> 01:23:39,296
- 對不起。
- 聽著，我得走了。嗯。拜拜
- I'm sorry.- Listen, I have to go. Yeah. Bye.

825
01:23:42,811 --> 01:23:45,265
我在想麥克有沒有和你提到……
I was wondering if Michael had ever mentioned anything to you...

826
01:23:45,356 --> 01:23:46,386
他以前的學校
about his old school.

827
01:23:46,732 --> 01:23:47,929
不多。怎麼問這個？
Not much. Why?

828
01:23:48,025 --> 01:23:49,850
都沒把他的檔案寄來。
They never sent his records.

829
01:23:51,028 --> 01:23:52,106
然後呢？
So?

830
01:23:52,446 --> 01:23:54,271
我打電話給學校，說沒有他的檔案。
I called the school.They have no record of him.

831
01:23:54,364 --> 01:23:57,529
有可能是電腦刪掉了，或者什麼的。
They probably got eaten by a computer,or something.

832
01:23:58,368 --> 01:24:01,320
在肯塔基州的藍山，沒有電腦的
They don't have a computer in Blue Hill, Kentucky.

833
01:24:02,580 --> 01:24:04,536
你研究他做什麼？
What are you on his case for?

834
01:24:05,582 --> 01:24:08,866
- 我們對他一無所知。
- 嗯，他以前是個殺人犯
- We know nothing about him.- So, he's an axe murderer.

835
01:24:09,127 --> 01:24:13,205
我說，拜託！我以為他是你教過的音樂最好的學生。
I mean, come on! I thought he was the best music student you ever had.

836
01:24:13,298 --> 01:24:16,131
他是，但這解釋不了他檔案丟失的問題
He is, but that doesn't explain his missing records.

837
01:24:17,468 --> 01:24:20,136
如果你想知道他究竟是誰，為什麼不直接找他談？
If you want to know who he is, why don't you talk to him?

838
01:24:20,930 --> 01:24:22,588
他是個人！
He's a person!

839
01:24:24,391 --> 01:24:26,465
他不是電腦裡的數據
He's not a computer printout!

840
01:24:33,441 --> 01:24:35,765
能不能把門關上？
Would you please close the door?

841
01:24:43,992 --> 01:24:45,022
- 曼菲爾德太太？
- 是
- Mrs. Manfield?- Yes.

842
01:24:45,244 --> 01:24:46,986
- 謝謝你能來
- 您好
- Thank you for coming.- How do you do?

843
01:24:47,079 --> 01:24:49,153
- 要不要來點咖啡？
- 不，謝謝
- Would you like some coffee?- No, thanks.

844
01:24:54,376 --> 01:24:56,166
我想和您聊聊麥克
I want to talk to you about Michael.

845
01:24:56,712 --> 01:24:59,830
我不想在學校見，這樣他就不知道我們談過
I didn't want to meet at school,because he doesn't know we're talking.

846
01:24:59,923 --> 01:25:01,795
但是他最近很失落也很緊張
But he's been upset lately, and nervous.

847
01:25:01,883 --> 01:25:04,123
我以為可能是家裡出了點事
I thought maybe there was something at home.

848
01:25:05,553 --> 01:25:06,583
沒有
No.

849
01:25:07,472 --> 01:25:11,550
我知道這是私人事情。我只是覺得如果我知道的話，我能幫得上忙。
I know these things are private. I just thought maybe I could help, if I knew.

850
01:25:11,975 --> 01:25:13,765
但是真的什麼事都沒有。
But there isn't anything. Really.

851
01:25:15,228 --> 01:25:17,349
也許他擔心朱利亞德。
Maybe he's worried about Juilliard.

852
01:25:18,982 --> 01:25:20,012
朱利亞德？
Juilliard?

853
01:25:21,192 --> 01:25:22,815
您知道他的計劃？
You know about his plans?

854
01:25:23,403 --> 01:25:26,023
- 是啊，當然
- 您不反對？
- Yeah, sure.- And you don't object?

855
01:25:26,531 --> 01:25:27,561
不反對
No.

856
01:25:28,574 --> 01:25:31,028
他們對他的面試印象深刻
They were very impressed with his audition.

857
01:25:33,036 --> 01:25:36,154
他們打算一拿到他的檔案就錄取他
They're prepared to take him, just as soon as they get his records.

858
01:25:39,250 --> 01:25:41,537
那時候他就得去了，是不是？
He'll have to go then, won't he?

859
01:25:42,545 --> 01:25:44,583
是不是經濟困難？
Is there a financial problem?

860
01:25:45,422 --> 01:25:47,828
我們可不像洛克菲勒家族那麼有錢。
We're not the Rockefellers.

861
01:25:48,342 --> 01:25:50,298
他可能會擔心錢的問題
He could be worried about that.

862
01:25:50,385 --> 01:25:52,008
我們還過得下去。
We always manage.

863
01:25:52,179 --> 01:25:54,847
有獎學金的。他可以拿
There are scholarships. He could get one.

864
01:25:55,056 --> 01:25:56,549
他很有才華
He's very talented.

865
01:25:56,891 --> 01:26:00,056
我們也許不富裕，但我們關心孩子
We may not have a lot, but we care about our kids.

866
01:26:00,144 --> 01:26:01,637
我當然知道您關心
I'm sure you do.

867
01:26:02,312 --> 01:26:06,178
我只是想知道他有過專業的老師麼？
I was just wondering,has he ever had a serious teacher?

868
01:26:07,150 --> 01:26:09,141
他是怎樣達到這個水平的？
How has he gotten this far?

869
01:26:09,236 --> 01:26:10,777
我不知道
I don't know.

870
01:26:10,862 --> 01:26:14,443
他在這學一點，那學一點。我們經常搬家。為什麼問這個
He's picked up a little here and there.We move around a lot. Why?

871
01:26:14,574 --> 01:26:17,573
我給藍山打了電話，沒有麥克·曼菲爾德的檔案
I called Blue Hill and they have no record of Michael Manfield.

872
01:26:22,831 --> 01:26:25,237
那是因為他在那註冊的時候沒有用曼菲爾德這個名字
That's because he wasn't registered there under Manfield.

873
01:26:25,583 --> 01:26:27,870
你看，我以前結過婚，保羅收養了他
See, I was married before,and Paul adopted him.

874
01:26:27,961 --> 01:26:30,877
但是直到今年才能合法地跟他的姓
But it took until just this year to adopt his name legally.

875
01:26:30,964 --> 01:26:33,632
在藍山，他跟的是我前夫的姓
He's under my old husband's name at Blue Hill.

876
01:26:34,675 --> 01:26:37,081
沒有這些檔案，他不能完成申請
He can't finish his application without those records.

877
01:26:37,178 --> 01:26:38,505
我會拿到的
I'll get them.

878
01:26:38,763 --> 01:26:41,679
你必須得拿，因為他們只把檔案給家長……
You'll have to, because they won't release them to anyone but a parent-

879
01:26:41,764 --> 01:26:44,170
我說了，我會拿到的。行了麼？
I said, I'll get them. All right?

880
01:26:46,352 --> 01:26:48,010
- 現在，我得走了
- 好的，當然
- Now, if you'll excuse me.
- Yeah, sure.

881
01:28:58,596 --> 01:29:00,089
怎麼了，媽媽？
What's wrong, Mom?

882
01:29:02,058 --> 01:29:03,136
沒什麼
Nothing.

883
01:29:06,395 --> 01:29:07,888
我愛你
I just love you.

884
01:29:25,913 --> 01:29:27,821
我要去接你爸爸
I've got to pick up your father.

885
01:29:40,467 --> 01:29:44,249
喜歡麼？我把貨車賣了，買了這個。我覺得這樣更實際一點。
Do you like it? I traded the van in for it.Thought it'd be more practical.

886
01:29:44,846 --> 01:29:46,802
而且，這讓他們一直猜測
Besides, it keeps them guessing.

887
01:29:57,316 --> 01:29:58,725
怎麼了，山姆？
What's up, Sam?

888
01:29:59,026 --> 01:30:00,684
別那麼叫我
Don't call me that.

889
01:30:01,778 --> 01:30:02,808
好吧
Okay.

890
01:30:07,575 --> 01:30:09,483
丹尼去申請大學了
Danny's applied to college.

891
01:30:11,996 --> 01:30:13,074
在哪？
Where?

892
01:30:13,372 --> 01:30:14,699
朱利亞德
Juilliard.

893
01:30:15,791 --> 01:30:16,952
你怎麼知道的？
How do you know?

894
01:30:17,042 --> 01:30:19,531
菲利普斯。他想讓他去
Phillips. He wants him to go.

895
01:30:22,005 --> 01:30:24,838
他為什麼不離咱們家的事遠點？
Why doesn't he keep his goddamn nose out of our business?

896
01:30:24,924 --> 01:30:26,915
因為他覺得他很有才華。
Because he thinks he's talented.

897
01:30:28,469 --> 01:30:29,926
丹尼告訴你這些了麼？
Has Danny told you about any of this?

898
01:30:31,263 --> 01:30:32,293
沒有。
No.

899
01:30:36,727 --> 01:30:38,268
我們要怎麼做？
What are we going to do?

900
01:30:38,812 --> 01:30:40,139
媽的
Shit.

901
01:30:40,814 --> 01:30:43,564
去他媽的！
Goddamn fucking shit!

902
01:30:44,316 --> 01:30:45,643
他為什麼不能去上大學？
Why can't he go?

903
01:30:45,943 --> 01:30:47,851
因為如果他去了，我們就再也見不到他了。
Because we'll never see him again if he does.

904
01:30:47,945 --> 01:30:50,232
為什麼不能？我們可以安排和他見面。
Why? We could arrange to meet him.

905
01:30:51,114 --> 01:30:52,441
你想這樣？
Is that what you want?

906
01:30:52,532 --> 01:30:57,192
在機場休息室見十分鐘，然後聯邦調查局一輩子跟在他屁股後面？
Ten minutes at an airport lounge, and the FBl all over his ass the rest of the time?

907
01:30:58,496 --> 01:31:01,946
你想讓他像我父母一樣站在電話亭，洗衣房……
You want him standing in phone booths and Laundromats like my parents...

908
01:31:02,083 --> 01:31:05,201
只能通過通信網絡和我們聯繫？我不想這樣。
only connecting with us through the network? I don't think so.

909
01:31:06,295 --> 01:31:08,619
如果他去了，我們就再也見不到他了
If he goes,we're never going to see him again...

910
01:31:09,255 --> 01:31:11,579
我不能接受。
and that is unacceptable to me.

911
01:31:21,475 --> 01:31:24,391
我連想都不會想。
I never even let myself think about this.

912
01:31:25,729 --> 01:31:28,053
我真傻。
I was so stupid.

913
01:31:30,733 --> 01:31:32,973
我只想讓我們在一起
All I wanted was that we would be together.

914
01:31:36,405 --> 01:31:39,357
我應該把丹尼扔給我媽媽的
We should have left Danny with my mother.

915
01:31:40,868 --> 01:31:43,108
- 我們都不該有哈利
- 閉嘴。
- We never should have had Harry.- Stop it.

916
01:31:43,203 --> 01:31:47,413
我不能這樣，阿瑟。看看我們對孩子都做了些什麼。
I can't, Arthur.Look what we're doing to these kids.

917
01:31:48,166 --> 01:31:50,490
他們一輩子都像罪犯一樣在逃亡。
They've been running their whole lives like criminals.

918
01:31:50,585 --> 01:31:51,912
他們什麼都沒做！
And they didn't do anything!

919
01:31:52,252 --> 01:31:53,449
這不公平
It isn't fair.

920
01:31:53,545 --> 01:31:55,869
我知道這他媽的不公平。
I know it isn't goddamned fair.

921
01:31:56,381 --> 01:32:00,329
他們經過了一些衝擊，但是你這樣逼自己於事無補
They've taken some bumps, but it's not going to help anything to beat yourself up.

922
01:32:02,387 --> 01:32:04,378
看看他們，看在上帝的份上。
Look at them, for God's sake.

923
01:32:04,472 --> 01:32:07,305
看看這些孩子。他們多麼優秀
Look at those kids. They're magnificent.

924
01:32:07,976 --> 01:32:09,469
他們很美
They're beautiful.

925
01:32:09,560 --> 01:32:11,634
很聰明很體貼
And bright. Caring.

926
01:32:12,814 --> 01:32:14,770
我們能做得多壞呢？
How badly could we have done?

927
01:32:18,401 --> 01:32:20,143
我們應該自首
We should turn ourselves in.

928
01:32:22,071 --> 01:32:24,643
然後接下來15年都呆在監獄裡……
So we can sit in prison for the next 15 years...

929
01:32:24,740 --> 01:32:27,027
從鐵窗裡看我們的孩子們？
and look at the kids through bars?

930
01:32:27,576 --> 01:32:31,026
每次還只能看一個小時
You can only get through this one day, one hour at a time.

931
01:32:32,331 --> 01:32:34,322
我就準備這麼做。
That's what I'm doing.

932
01:32:36,042 --> 01:32:38,033
丹尼已經長大了。
And Danny's all grown up.

933
01:32:41,672 --> 01:32:43,129
我們該放他走了
We have to let him go.

934
01:32:52,975 --> 01:32:54,883
這顆牙疼死我了
This tooth is killing me.

935
01:32:54,976 --> 01:32:58,141
我覺得補的東西掉了。該去看看喬納。
I think I lost a filling. Better go see Jonah.

936
01:32:59,646 --> 01:33:01,139
我會坐公交車。
I'll take a bus.

937
01:33:01,732 --> 01:33:03,889
- 你去市內的時候我總是擔心
- 為什麼？
- I always worry when you go into the city.- Why?

938
01:33:04,401 --> 01:33:06,392
因為在那他們誰都能看見
Because that's where they get everyone.

939
01:33:06,653 --> 01:33:08,146
很安靜。
It's been quiet.

940
01:33:09,489 --> 01:33:11,480
有時候太安靜了
Sometimes it gets too quiet.

941
01:33:11,908 --> 01:33:14,148
你還記得孩子小時候你常說的話麼？
Remember what you used to say when the kids were small?

942
01:33:14,327 --> 01:33:16,651
「別著急，除非你什麼都聽不見了。」
"Don't worry unless you don't hear anything. "

943
01:33:17,497 --> 01:33:19,322
小心點，好不好？
Be careful, all right?

944
01:33:29,841 --> 01:33:32,793
我什麼都沒看見。X光片裡也什麼都沒有。
I don't see anything. And there's nothing on the x-ray.

945
01:33:32,885 --> 01:33:34,543
我沒在抱怨。
I'm not complaining.

946
01:33:37,181 --> 01:33:38,722
還需要什麼嗎？
You need anything else?

947
01:33:40,726 --> 01:33:44,389
不，謝謝。我們很好。我在為一個全科醫生工作。
No, thanks. We're okay. I'm working for a GP.

948
01:33:45,229 --> 01:33:46,722
現金可以嗎？
How about cash?

949
01:33:47,815 --> 01:33:48,976
可以
Okay.

950
01:33:50,734 --> 01:33:54,730
如果你提前告訴我，我可以安排更多的
If you'd give me some notice, I could arrange to have more.

951
01:33:54,988 --> 01:33:57,656
不。很好了。謝謝
No. This is great. Thanks.

952
01:33:59,326 --> 01:34:02,325
- 你總是讓我覺得這麼愧疚。
- 為什麼？
- You always make me feel so guilty. - Why?

953
01:34:02,579 --> 01:34:04,120
這就是你的生活方式。
You're living it.

954
01:34:04,663 --> 01:34:07,331
是啊，我猜我是。
Yeah, I guess I am.

955
01:34:09,334 --> 01:34:13,164
喬納，我需要你幫我打個電話
Jonah, I need youabcto make a phone call for me.

956
01:34:14,047 --> 01:34:15,244
當然可以
Of course.

957
01:34:23,765 --> 01:34:24,795
夫人？
Madame?

958
01:34:52,331 --> 01:34:53,492
嗨，爸爸
Hi, Dad.

959
01:34:57,336 --> 01:34:59,493
我讓喬納做的這個
I asked Jonah to set this up.

960
01:35:04,718 --> 01:35:06,460
如果你想，可以叫警察
You can call the cops if you want to.

961
01:35:15,310 --> 01:35:16,851
對不起。
I'm sorry.

962
01:35:19,189 --> 01:35:21,014
這對我也很難
This is hard for me, too.

963
01:35:23,485 --> 01:35:26,153
- 夫人要點什麼飲料？
- 不，謝謝
- Will madame have a drink?- No, thank you.

964
01:35:33,286 --> 01:35:36,202
我想知道14年不見你的孩子
I wonder if you'll ever know what it's like...

965
01:35:36,288 --> 01:35:38,991
是什麼感覺
not to see your child for 14 years.

966
01:35:42,377 --> 01:35:45,210
連他是死是活都不知道
Not knowing whether she's living or dead.

967
01:35:52,553 --> 01:35:53,880
不知道這孩子是不是
Not knowing whether that child...

968
01:35:54,805 --> 01:35:59,264
要對別人的死亡或者傷殘負責
is responsible for the death and mutilation of other human beings.

969
01:36:01,143 --> 01:36:03,632
要不要讓你自己
Whether to hold yourself responsible...

970
01:36:04,146 --> 01:36:05,971
為那死亡或傷殘負責任
for that death and mutilation...

971
01:36:06,524 --> 01:36:10,437
因為扣動扳機，引爆炸彈的是你的孩子
because it is your child who is pulling the triggers, setting the bombs.

972
01:36:10,527 --> 01:36:12,518
我沒殺任何人
I didn't kill anybody.

973
01:36:15,198 --> 01:36:18,861
我不是來為自己辯護或是談政治的
I didn't come here to defend myself or to talk politics.

974
01:36:20,035 --> 01:36:24,779
如果你不相信我當時那麼做是出於良心要結束戰爭
If you don't believe by now that what I did was an act of conscience to stop the war...

975
01:36:25,207 --> 01:36:28,290
那我說什麼你都不會明白
then there's nothing I can say to you that's going to make you understand.

976
01:36:28,377 --> 01:36:30,368
一個人失明，還殘疾了
A man was blinded and paralyzed.

977
01:36:30,462 --> 01:36:32,204
他本不該在那的。
He wasn't supposed to be there.

978
01:36:36,718 --> 01:36:38,175
你不覺得，有些時候
Don't you think there have been times...

979
01:36:38,261 --> 01:36:41,177
我寧願讓自己失明，讓自己殘疾，來挽回這一切麼？
that I would have blinded and paralyzed myself to take that back?

980
01:36:41,471 --> 01:36:43,047
那都是阿瑟的影響。
It's all Arthur's influence.

981
01:36:43,140 --> 01:36:44,798
不，爸爸，不是
No, Dad, it isn't.

982
01:36:45,684 --> 01:36:47,058
是我的主意。
It was my idea.

983
01:36:47,644 --> 01:36:50,133
我活在我自己的選擇帶來的後果中
I'm living with the consequences of my own choice.

984
01:36:50,230 --> 01:36:52,102
- 我不信。
- 那是你的問題
- I don't believe it.- Well, that's your problem.

985
01:36:52,190 --> 01:36:53,766
你媽媽和我……
Your mother and me...

986
01:36:55,026 --> 01:36:56,567
你為我們考慮過麼？
Do you think about us?

987
01:37:03,491 --> 01:37:06,027
- 你非得這麼問麼
- 對。
- Do you really have to ask that?- Yes.

988
01:37:11,707 --> 01:37:14,196
上一次我記得你對我說
The last thing I remember you saying to me...

989
01:37:15,628 --> 01:37:18,034
我是個帝國主義的蠢豬
was that I was an imperialist pig...

990
01:37:18,297 --> 01:37:23,290
一個人為了戰爭，貧窮和種族主義承擔責任
personally responsible for the war, the spread of poverty, racism.

991
01:37:24,553 --> 01:37:26,176
- 我還年輕
- 是
- I was young.- Yes.

992
01:37:29,890 --> 01:37:31,715
你還年輕
You were young.

993
01:37:33,227 --> 01:37:34,554
有才華
And talented.

994
01:37:36,563 --> 01:37:37,641
美麗
And beautiful.

995
01:37:38,982 --> 01:37:40,807
那麼充滿了愛
And so full of love.

996
01:37:43,528 --> 01:37:46,860
上帝啊，安妮。你為什麼把它們都拋棄了？
My God, Annie.Why did you throw it all away?

997
01:37:53,161 --> 01:37:56,326
你媽媽很想你。還有丹尼
Your mother misses you terribly. And Danny.

998
01:38:01,044 --> 01:38:02,702
你會收留他麼，爸爸
Will you take him, Dad?

999
01:38:05,381 --> 01:38:07,004
他想學音樂
He wants to study music.

1000
01:38:07,883 --> 01:38:09,376
他很好
He's good.

1001
01:38:09,884 --> 01:38:11,590
他們想讓他去朱利亞德
They want him at Juilliard.

1002
01:38:13,721 --> 01:38:15,629
就像他們當時想讓你一樣
Just like they wanted you.

1003
01:38:19,060 --> 01:38:21,466
你還有那個用來練習的板？
Do you still have that practice board?

1004
01:38:22,730 --> 01:38:26,228
一直到現在。丹尼就是在那上面學會彈琴。
So far. Danny learned to play piano on it.

1005
01:38:28,068 --> 01:38:29,726
你教他的？
So you taught him?

1006
01:38:33,322 --> 01:38:36,321
不覺得這有點諷刺麼？
There's some irony in this, don't you think?

1007
01:38:38,035 --> 01:38:39,492
你現在在這
Here you are...

1008
01:38:40,204 --> 01:38:42,528
求我把丹尼帶到
asking me to take Danny...

1009
01:38:43,373 --> 01:38:47,583
你曾經唯恐避之不及的人生裡
into a life that you ran from like a shot out of hell.

1010
01:38:50,213 --> 01:38:51,919
他真的想要麼？
Is this what he wants?

1011
01:38:52,006 --> 01:38:53,499
我覺得是
I think so.

1012
01:38:53,883 --> 01:38:56,882
他沒告訴我就自己去了面試
He got himself an audition without telling me.

1013
01:38:59,679 --> 01:39:03,342
他會需要錢和照顧他的人
He'll need money, and people to care for him.

1014
01:39:04,559 --> 01:39:06,799
你不覺得你要的太多了麼？
Don't you think this is too much to ask?

1015
01:39:07,979 --> 01:39:09,804
我幾乎不認識這男孩
I hardly know the boy.

1016
01:39:11,899 --> 01:39:13,392
如果我們收留了他
If we take him...

1017
01:39:16,237 --> 01:39:19,936
那我們去哪都會有聯邦調查局的人跟著
there'd be FBl agents following us everywhere we go.

1018
01:39:21,282 --> 01:39:22,656
你就再也見不到他
You'd never be able to see him.

1019
01:39:24,702 --> 01:39:26,360
我們太老了，不能這麼做了
We're too old for this.

1020
01:39:28,164 --> 01:39:32,030
嗯，我覺得我要的太多了
Yeah, I think it's too much to ask.

1021
01:39:38,798 --> 01:39:40,456
我還有一個兒子
I have another son.

1022
01:39:41,175 --> 01:39:43,499
他十歲。叫哈利。
He's 10. Harry.

1023
01:39:45,512 --> 01:39:47,337
我在新聞上聽說了
I heard about it on the news.

1024
01:39:49,349 --> 01:39:51,007
我打算
I plan to turn myself in...

1025
01:39:51,101 --> 01:39:54,931
在他再也不需要我的時候就去自首，在他足夠大的時候
when he doesn't need me anymore.When he's old enough.

1026
01:39:55,689 --> 01:39:57,016
阿瑟呢？
And Arthur?

1027
01:39:57,524 --> 01:39:59,100
我不能為他說話
I can't speak for him.

1028
01:40:03,111 --> 01:40:04,936
請你考慮考慮
Please think about this.

1029
01:40:12,871 --> 01:40:14,280
我該走了
I should go.

1030
01:40:17,333 --> 01:40:18,363
安妮。
Annie.

1031
01:40:21,796 --> 01:40:23,502
他可以來我們家
He can come to us.

1032
01:40:39,478 --> 01:40:42,228
請您告訴媽媽，我愛她
Please, tell Mom that I love her.

1033
01:40:44,149 --> 01:40:46,389
我經常想你倆
And I've thought about you both so often.

1034
01:40:47,777 --> 01:40:49,768
我把你叫出來。
I've called out to you.

1035
01:40:52,406 --> 01:40:55,738
對不起我給你們帶來這麼多痛苦
I'm sorry that I've caused you so much pain.

1036
01:41:00,497 --> 01:41:03,165
我猜我要知道這是什麼感覺了
I guess I'm about to see what it feels like.

1037
01:41:08,587 --> 01:41:09,784
我愛你，爸爸
I love you, Dad.

1038
01:41:46,163 --> 01:41:47,988
我去見了我父親
I saw my father.

1039
01:41:50,000 --> 01:41:51,161
你什麼？
You what?

1040
01:41:51,668 --> 01:41:53,493
我見了唐納德
I saw Donald.

1041
01:41:55,671 --> 01:41:58,670
你就那麼走進他辦公室坐在他桌邊？
You just walked into his office and sat down at his desk?

1042
01:41:58,883 --> 01:41:59,913
沒有
No.

1043
01:42:00,050 --> 01:42:03,667
我在「小鍋」和他吃了午飯
I had lunch with him at La Petite Marmite.

1044
01:42:04,805 --> 01:42:06,002
幹什麼？
What for?

1045
01:42:07,182 --> 01:42:09,173
想看看他要不要收留丹尼.
To see if he'd take Danny.

1046
01:42:10,018 --> 01:42:11,676
收留丹尼？
Take Danny?

1047
01:42:12,187 --> 01:42:14,143
這樣他就可以上大學了
So he can go to college.

1048
01:42:15,981 --> 01:42:17,308
你開玩笑吧
You're kidding.

1049
01:42:18,567 --> 01:42:20,060
他說他會的
He said he would.

1050
01:42:20,902 --> 01:42:22,560
他說他會？
He said he would?

1051
01:42:23,738 --> 01:42:25,943
你知不知道會發生什麼？
You know what could have happened?

1052
01:42:27,992 --> 01:42:30,149
菲利普斯要你這麼做的？
Did Phillips put you up to this?

1053
01:42:30,286 --> 01:42:32,657
沒人要求我這麼做
Nobody put me up to this.

1054
01:42:33,915 --> 01:42:36,914
和菲利普斯無關。這是為了丹尼。
It's not about Phillips. It's about Danny.

1055
01:42:37,250 --> 01:42:41,198
他想去。他申請了，去了面試。
He wants to go. He applied.He went to an audition.

1056
01:42:41,296 --> 01:42:44,165
- 他他媽的去哪了？
- 朱利亞德
- He went fucking where?- Juilliard.

1057
01:42:46,676 --> 01:42:48,418
我不相信我的耳朵。
I don't believe my ears.

1058
01:42:48,511 --> 01:42:50,502
就給他一次機會吧。
Just give him a chance.

1059
01:42:51,055 --> 01:42:54,138
我要給黛博拉打電話，看看她能不能假造些檔案
I'm going to call Deborah and see if she can make him up some records.

1060
01:42:54,225 --> 01:42:55,422
為什麼？
Why?

1061
01:42:55,517 --> 01:42:58,185
因為菲力普斯給我填在申請表上的學校打了電話Because Phillips called the school I put on the registration form...

1062
01:42:58,270 --> 01:43:00,391
然後他們告訴他沒有叫麥克·曼菲爾德的人
and they told him there was no Michael Manfield.

1063
01:43:00,521 --> 01:43:02,512
會沒事的。
It's going to be okay.

1064
01:43:02,732 --> 01:43:05,221
他可以及時做好檔案的。阿瑟！
He can get records made up in time. Artie!

1065
01:43:08,737 --> 01:43:10,977
我們要搬了，孩子們
We're moving base camp, kids.

1066
01:43:12,157 --> 01:43:13,982
再呆幾天，我們就走。
We have a few days, and we're gone.

1067
01:43:14,493 --> 01:43:15,986
把蹤跡都銷毀掉。
Cover your tracks.

1068
01:43:16,453 --> 01:43:17,780
聽見沒？
You hear me?

1069
01:43:19,289 --> 01:43:21,161
你有想告訴我的事麼？
You have anything you want to tell me?

1070
01:43:21,623 --> 01:43:22,736
沒有。
No.

1071
01:43:22,833 --> 01:43:23,946
好。
Good.

1072
01:43:42,560 --> 01:43:44,385
我爸爸想要搬走。
My father wants to move on.

1073
01:43:50,567 --> 01:43:51,680
為什麼？
Why?

1074
01:43:52,819 --> 01:43:54,525
他有眼見。
He gets a sense.

1075
01:43:57,239 --> 01:43:58,400
就那樣？
Just like that?

1076
01:43:59,158 --> 01:44:00,651
就那樣。
Just like that.

1077
01:44:04,163 --> 01:44:05,324
什麼時候？
When?

1078
01:44:06,414 --> 01:44:07,492
隨時。
Anytime.

1079
01:44:08,583 --> 01:44:10,408
你就那麼消失了？
You'll just disappear?

1080
01:44:18,175 --> 01:44:19,668
那我們怎麼辦？
What about us?

1081
01:44:22,804 --> 01:44:25,175
- 他們需要我。
- 我需要你！
- They need me.- I need you!

1082
01:44:27,267 --> 01:44:29,009
你沒和他們談？
You didn't talk to them?

1083
01:44:32,813 --> 01:44:36,227
你不能一直逃離你沒有責任的事
You can't keep running from something you had nothing to do with.

1084
01:44:36,566 --> 01:44:38,723
你應該有你自己的機會
You deserve your own chance.

1085
01:44:53,164 --> 01:44:55,570
- 我想和你談談
- 沒什麼可談的
- I want to talk to you.- There's nothing to talk about.

1086
01:44:55,667 --> 01:44:57,076
菲利普斯知道的太多了
Phillips knows too much.

1087
01:44:57,168 --> 01:44:59,492
你在讓你的情感影響你的判斷。
You were letting your feelings affect your judgment.

1088
01:44:59,754 --> 01:45:01,745
而且，這就是上學
Besides, it's academic.

1089
01:45:14,058 --> 01:45:15,599
沒人會說的
Nobody will talk.

1090
01:45:16,102 --> 01:45:17,263
你不知道。
You don't know that.

1091
01:45:18,521 --> 01:45:21,189
他們能抓的都會抓。
They're going to try to pick up everyone they can now.

1092
01:45:23,442 --> 01:45:24,721
我們在這的日子到頭了。
We're finished here.

1093
01:45:33,034 --> 01:45:35,570
- 我們可以慢慢收手的，不是麼？
- 我們必須走了
- We can close up shop slowly, can't we?- We'll have to.

1094
01:45:35,828 --> 01:45:38,496
不然就會引起注意
Otherwise we'll attract attention.

1095
01:45:39,414 --> 01:45:41,868
大家都去上班和上學，等接下來的通知
Everybody goes to work and school until further notice.

1096
01:45:41,959 --> 01:45:45,161
如果有問題我們就在80號公路附近的野餐區見面
If there's a problem,will meet at the picnic area near Route 80.

1097
01:45:45,253 --> 01:45:48,667
還沒有理由覺得他們在追捕我們，所以冷靜
There's no reason to think they're onto us yet, so stay calm.

1098
01:46:09,692 --> 01:46:12,691
- 爸爸，我能和你說一會話麼？
- 現在不行。
- Dad, can I talk to you a minute?- Not now.

1099
01:46:19,325 --> 01:46:21,233
我想留下。
I was thinking about staying.

1100
01:46:21,452 --> 01:46:24,238
- 你不得去上課麼？
- 還有半個小時
- Don't you have school?- In half an hour.

1101
01:46:41,388 --> 01:46:42,501
我想留下。
I want to stay.

1102
01:46:43,931 --> 01:46:45,092
留下？
Stay?

1103
01:46:47,100 --> 01:46:49,221
你覺得現在是討論這個問題的時候麼
Do you think this is a good time to discuss this?

1104
01:46:50,520 --> 01:46:52,926
我們現在不能說。我們遇到麻煩了。
We can't talk now. We're in trouble here.

1105
01:46:54,274 --> 01:46:55,731
我告訴你了！
I taught you!

1106
01:46:56,151 --> 01:46:58,640
我告訴你了！我們不能打破我們之間的聯繫
I taught you! We cannot break rank.

1107
01:46:59,279 --> 01:47:01,519
一個集體的能力是由它最弱的一環決定的
A unit is only as good as its weakest link.

1108
01:47:01,614 --> 01:47:02,811
我們是一個集體！
We're a unit!

1109
01:47:05,158 --> 01:47:07,647
這些都是我教你的，不記得了麼？
I taught you all of this,don't you remember that?

1110
01:47:09,746 --> 01:47:11,322
我不想聽你
I don't want to hear you talking about this...

1111
01:47:11,414 --> 01:47:13,370
在你媽媽或者你弟弟面前說這些，聽見沒有？
in front of your mother or your brother, do you hear me?

1112
01:47:13,458 --> 01:47:14,951
我說，聽見沒有？
I said, do you hear me?

1113
01:47:17,211 --> 01:47:19,083
這回說完了沒？
Are we finished talking about this now?

1114
01:47:26,844 --> 01:47:27,874
泰勒女士
Mrs. Taylor.

1115
01:47:29,514 --> 01:47:31,386
把所有東西都拿出來，穿上袍子就行
Just remove everything and put on the gown.

1116
01:47:31,474 --> 01:47:33,180
幾分鐘內就可以見醫生了
The doctor will see you in a few minutes.

1117
01:47:35,102 --> 01:47:38,350
好的。我馬上就回來給你稱體重
All right. I'll be right back to weigh you.

1118
01:47:39,023 --> 01:47:41,180
能幫我拉拉鏈麼，親愛的？
Could you help me with this zipper, dear?

1119
01:47:43,610 --> 01:47:46,230
你知道昨晚伊利莎白·鮑威爾怎麼了麼？
Did you hear what happened to Elizabeth Powell last night?

1120
01:47:46,363 --> 01:47:47,393
不知道
No, I didn't.

1121
01:47:47,781 --> 01:47:49,938
聯邦調查局找她了
The FBl came to see her.

1122
01:47:50,783 --> 01:47:53,023
搶銀行，還殺死了警察的那次
The car that was used in that bank robbery...

1123
01:47:53,619 --> 01:47:55,160
他們用的車
where they killed those policemen...

1124
01:47:55,245 --> 01:47:57,734
是用她的信用卡租的
it was rented with her credit card.

1125
01:47:58,373 --> 01:47:59,830
你相信麼？
Can you believe it?

1126
01:48:00,333 --> 01:48:04,329
他們怎麼能拿到她的卡？她自己都從來不用。
How could they have got hold of her card? She never even uses it herself.

1127
01:48:04,504 --> 01:48:08,630
這就是為什麼她沒注意到卡不見了
That's how come she didn't notice it was gone.

1128
01:48:09,717 --> 01:48:11,708
那些人是一幫惡棍，泰勒女士
Those people are crooks, Mrs. Taylor.

1129
01:48:11,802 --> 01:48:14,042
他們很有可能就是從通訊錄裡查出她的電話
They probably just took her name out of the phone book...

1130
01:48:14,137 --> 01:48:15,416
然後假造了一張卡。
and made up a false card.

1131
01:48:15,889 --> 01:48:17,679
能想像這多背運麼？
Can you imagine the bad luck?

1132
01:48:27,191 --> 01:48:30,356
請找保羅·曼菲爾德先生。我是他妻子。
Paul Manfield, please. His wife.

1133
01:48:33,696 --> 01:48:35,237
我們很著急。
We're in a hurry.

1134
01:48:35,365 --> 01:48:39,147
格斯從我一個病人那偷了信用卡。他用它來租車。
Gus took plastic from one of my patients.He used it to rent the car.

1135
01:48:50,212 --> 01:48:53,081
真的？我要去抽根煙
Frankie? I'm going out for a smoke.

1136
01:49:09,980 --> 01:49:13,312
- 我們著急麼，媽媽？
- 嗯。我們得找到丹尼。
- Are we in a hurry, Mom?- Yeah. We have to get Danny.

1137
01:49:19,654 --> 01:49:21,728
希望你丈夫還好。
I hope your husband is all right.

1138
01:49:29,789 --> 01:49:31,116
好了，走吧
Okay, let's go.

1139
01:49:31,207 --> 01:49:33,364
- 媽媽，我在那見你
- 我們時間不多。
- Mom, I'll meet you there.- We don't have much time.

1140
01:49:39,048 --> 01:49:43,258
塞林格在《麥田里的守望者》中用意象……
Salinger uses imagery in Catcher in the Rye to-

1141
